But Sir, in the Van of particulars, your care of that Religion profeſt in your Mother Church opens our arms, and Encircles you in Embraces as faſt, and durable, as thoſe with which you Embraced it: That Religion of which you uſe to ſay;


Illa meos, primum quae me ſibi junxit, amores

Abſtulit, illa habeat ſecum-ſervatque Sepulcro.
